Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏降临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算黑暗吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那持续闪烁的星屑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像朝阳那般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以寻找冥王之壶为目标而旅行的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到一个名为比赞迪的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位名叫拉多库的商人要雇佣我们作为护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到理由竟然是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随欧泽鲁所带冥王之壶一起传达的祖玛的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不想死的话 就雇佣莉娜.因巴斯”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 被祖玛盯上 又受到魔族袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊 谁来给我说明下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Town scape 因为是人造的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混身酸疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一起挤地板睡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为拉多库边上的房间值得期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是仓库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能及时应对祖玛的来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔是这么安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种安排真让人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真悠闲啊 我连昨天的疲劳都没消除呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些魔族可是相当的麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那些家伙的来袭 有什么想法吗 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊 虽然能想到好几个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟壶有关 跟祖玛有关 或是别的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会又在哪儿结怨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 至少跟古杜萨和迪古尔德是第一次碰面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 迷题很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且祖玛还没出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次祖玛好像有点拐弯抹角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令欧泽鲁把冥王之壶和信息带给拉多库
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条信息又命令我们去护卫拉多库
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖玛 拉多库 欧泽鲁 壶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 你就不用多想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 调查欧泽鲁不是最快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也非常在意壶里的雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 非常明显的可疑点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 人吓人吓死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 见门开着 我就擅自进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:03:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 老爷叫你们马上前往客厅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没感觉到她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能消除气息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是普通人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然睡到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这期间 祖玛突然来袭怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说祖玛会先来找我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且我们就在隔壁 很快就能赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不随时待在我的视线范围内就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子的护卫 壶可不会给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那个态度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个壶就那么臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性命被人盯上了 紧张也很正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就网开一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有高里和波克塔在护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉多库应该会安心一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那个大叔没碰过这种事 也许真是个好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能只是讨厌莉娜而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 肯定就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会相信你们这些骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲居然也会相信自己被人盯上了 真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是希望你们尽早滚出这个府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意跑来说这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是略加限制你们一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没人监视你们就捣乱的话 绝对不会放过你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 父子两人都是一个德行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在祖玛出现之前 只能稍加忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 这是女仆的份内事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐似乎没吃完 不合您口味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 只是没食欲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚餐我就少做点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲什么时候再去旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 没听提起过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去问一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是乔康达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着是祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是拉多库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地换主人 而且好像有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本是为了保护封印雷藏灵魂的壶才会到处转移吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:07:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 为什么又要我们破坏掉壶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 只有行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护卫交给阿梅莉亚和杰路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去调查欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到护卫工作真清闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜不在身边 祖玛也不会来袭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来下国际象棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄凤蝶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啊 看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算为您做件冬装
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以量一下拉多库老爷的尺寸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为女仆 你只要做好府邸里的事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他无需过问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁果然很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟踪她有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能打听些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之先跟着她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小欧啊 谢谢你帮我捡起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好吃的水果 要尝尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要尝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在出去就露陷了 露陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 水分很多很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个好像也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要尝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在出去就露陷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢哪个就拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个都拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这的鱼非常新鲜哦 拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都这样 不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有上好的肉哦 来 免费送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 多谢关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小欧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 小欧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在像你这种懂礼貌的孩子很少了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉多库先生找了个不错的女仆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有人气啊 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人你眼光真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是世界上独一无二的壶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟壶有仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你欠我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有很多理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我一下吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你们在跟踪我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你们我才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法分辨苹果和橘子的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想像人类一样 选择出较好的一个 该如何做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便怎样都可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个都选就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惑也是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 人类也会迷惑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 刚才为什么要破坏壶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近看到壶总有种不可思议的感觉 不由自主就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了 跟踪也露陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 我有很多事要问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖玛想干吗 为什么如此拐弯抹角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我只是奉祖玛大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将壶带到拉多库老爷那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要接受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有拒绝的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道你在保护冥王之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你为什么又叫我们破坏壶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想保护壶 可又口是心非
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 为什么不说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是发条停了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还没到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你们早晚会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像在和某处的某人说话一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人说到我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 再换个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前 魔族袭击了我们 你有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都行 知道就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊 线索…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么变得沮丧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果关键的地方还是一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜他们调查到欧泽鲁的秘密了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 也许很棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反悔了好多次了 不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 这边也不能再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪古尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古杜萨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 继续上次的话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 有事要问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为祖玛 还是因为壶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你们的所言我们是初次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾和那些毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的生命将在此终结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 上了哦 阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这次由我来提问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让沉睡在冥王之壶中雷藏灵魂苏醒的方法是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拯救塔夫拉希亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只被赋予了保护壶的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 让雷藏大人的灵魂苏醒 就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…是祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那边的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出现了啊 祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了啊 如你所愿 来到这个城镇了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你了 我将用态度来表达我的谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炎球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢 波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和祖玛还是一伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 契约已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来帮我们吧 你还欠我一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不在的话 你也会麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍我的人就要消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈闪枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的招数已经看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是看透了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈闪枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 还有什么要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵王结魔弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一招是没用的 先从你开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是契约
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炎矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚无障界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那边发出的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钟楼 发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然变成这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗持续太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们捡了一条命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔族呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也受伤了 胜负要到下次决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 不是祖玛 又是魔族来袭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过肯定是麻烦的对手没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们之前都在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一直不在府邸内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才被魔族袭击了 一直在结界里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔族 说的好像真的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是跑到哪里偷懒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我们一直战斗到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙好像扔下工作不知道跑去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算瞒过了自卫团 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了欧泽鲁的声望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那样还要继续雇佣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说父亲太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因此失去重要的东西我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来晚了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人一起行动会比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以了 去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人为什么要互相伤害 为什么要流泪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是黑暗并没有回答任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 秀逗魔导士 进化-R
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uncover 暴露的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话我会发飙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

